---
title: Articles
description: Writing on React, Three.js, frontend engineering, and building interactive 3D web experiences.
layout: simple
layout_title: Articles
layout_description: Writing on React, Three.js, frontend engineering, and interactive 3D web experiences.
---

{% assign english_posts = site.posts | where_exp: "p", "p.lang != 'id'" %}

{% if english_posts.size > 0 %}
<div class="flex max-w-3xl flex-col space-y-12">
  {% assign post = english_posts.first %}
  {% include post.liquid post=post badge="new" %}
  <div class="space-y-16">
    {% assign favorites = english_posts | where: "favorite", true | sort: "index" %}
    {% for post in favorites %}
      {% include post.liquid post=post badge="favorite" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 md:border-l md:border-gray-100 md:pl-6">
    <div class="flex max-w-3xl flex-col space-y-16">
      {% for post in english_posts %}
        {% include post.liquid post=post date=true %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% else %}
<div class="max-w-2xl">
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">English articles are coming soon. In the meantime, you can read my existing writing in Bahasa Indonesia.</p>
  <a href="/id/blog/" class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">Read Indonesian articles →</a>
</div>
{% endif %}
